    "There were no adverse events in either program (HIIT and MICT) during the exercise interventions.",
    "Thus, HIIT protocols proved to be a safe, effective, and pleasant tool for low-risk patients with CAD as well.",
    "This study represents a pioneering endeavor as the first RCT to systematically investigate the impact of communitybased exercise CR programs on various health-related parameters, lifestyle modifications, and the evolution of cardiovascular risk factors at both the 6-and 12-month post-intervention time points.",
